    "name": "Swiftdrop API",
    "description": "Complete test suite for the Swiftdrop last-mile delivery tracking API.\n\n## Setup\n1. Run `pnpm seed` (or `npm run seed`) to insert demo data.\n2. Import this collection into Postman.\n3. The `baseUrl` and `apiKey` variables are pre-configured.\n\n## Seed data overview\n\n### Agents\n| Variable | Name | Phone | Status |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| {{agentMarcus}} | Marcus Webb | +44-demo-0001 | UNAVAILABLE (active deliveries) |\n| {{agentSofia}} | Sofia Patel | +44-demo-0002 | available |\n| {{agentJordan}} | Jordan Okafor | +44-demo-0003 | UNAVAILABLE (off duty) |\n| {{agentPriya}} | Priya Nair | +44-demo-0004 | available (2 completed) |\n| {{agentElias}} | Elias Frost | +44-demo-0005 | available (no deliveries) |\n\n### Parcels\n| Variable | Tracking | Status | Agent |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| {{parcel1}} | TRK-2026-0001 | registered | — |\n| {{parcel2}} | TRK-2026-0002 | registered | — |\n| {{parcel3}} | TRK-2026-0003 | picked_up | Marcus Webb |\n| {{parcel4}} | TRK-2026-0004 | out_for_delivery | Marcus Webb |\n| {{parcel5}} | TRK-2026-0005 | delivered | Priya Nair (4 events) |\n| {{parcel6}} | TRK-2026-0006 | delivered | Priya Nair (4 events) |\n| {{parcel7}} | TRK-2026-0007 | failed | Marcus Webb |\n| {{parcel8}} | TRK-2026-0008 | failed | — |\n\n## Re-seeding\nMutating requests (assign, retry, update status, log event) change DB state. Re-run `pnpm seed` to reset.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
